  <brief_title>Measuring Temperatures of Tissues During Endoscopy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Measuring Temperatures of Tumors and Normal Tissues in the GI Tract, Using a Thermocouple Sheathed in a Catheter, in the Work Canal of an Endoscope</official_title>
  <sponsors>
